properties.sfomuseum:description: Children’s inflight activity kit issued by TWA:a. booklet; black cover with illustration of Space Shuttle; includes illustrated pages of various games, iron-on transfer, puppets, jokes and riddles, poster and a captain's cap;b. activity magazine; stapled pages describing Airshow Activity Kit contents; contains illustrated pages of games, iron-on transfer, puppets, jokes and riddles, poster and Kennedy Space Center facts.
